      "updated": 1770715904946,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "6️⃣ Final corrected architecture diagram in words\nWSGI\n\nClient → Gunicorn\n          ├── Worker 1 → Request A (blocking)\n          ├── Worker 2 → Request B\n\n\nASGI\nClient → Gunicorn\n          ├── Uvicorn Worker\n                ├── Request A (await)\n                ├── Request B (await)\n                ├── Request C (await)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "6️⃣ Final corrected architecture diagram in words\nWSGI\n\nClient → Gunicorn\n          ├── Worker 1 → Request A (blocking)\n          ├── Worker 2 → Request B\n\n\nASGI\nClient → Gunicorn\n          ├── Uvicorn Worker\n                ├── Request A (await)\n                ├── Request B (await)\n                ├── Request C (await)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "5LEXC4NI0CgptA4uQeR2b",
