      "updated": 1770716108428,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "7️⃣ One-liner you can use in interviews 🎯\n\n“WSGI scales by adding more OS processes, while ASGI scales by allowing one\n process to interleave multiple I/O-bound requests using async/await.”\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "7️⃣ One-liner you can use in interviews 🎯\n\n“WSGI scales by adding more OS processes, while ASGI scales by allowing one\n process to interleave multiple I/O-bound requests using async/await.”\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "cxAIUdyISFrq53HZm05xs",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1976.3490983576967,
      "y": 10100.51949784308,
      "width": 1584,
      "height": 5050,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
