      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773235365038,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "5️⃣ Threaded Workers (Exception)\nSome WSGI servers allow threads per worker.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "5️⃣ Threaded Workers (Exception)\nSome WSGI servers allow threads per worker.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QQHW5Dd0LcfiiikWwK9jQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1972.6733171076967,
      "y": 3771.499966593081,
      "width": 363,
      "height": 375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFD",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 702314469,
      "version": 171,
      "versionNonce": 753991257,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773235365038,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Gunicorn\nworker_class = gthread\nthreads = 4\n\n1 worker → 4 threads → 4 requests\n\nWorker1\n   Thread1 → Request1\n   Thread2 → Request2\n   Thread3 → Request3\n   Thread4 → Request4\n\nBut still:\nthreads share memory\nCPU bound tasks still block",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Gunicorn\nworker_class = gthread\nthreads = 4\n\n1 worker → 4 threads → 4 requests\n\nWorker1\n   Thread1 → Request1\n   Thread2 → Request2\n   Thread3 → Request3\n   Thread4 → Request4\n\nBut still:\nthreads share memory\nCPU bound tasks still block",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qoNvjzvSGRLhMih5mask3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1898.4584733576967,
      "y": 4184.230435343081,
      "width": 726,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFE",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1287437323,
      "version": 161,
      "versionNonce": 1792133945,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773235365038,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "6️⃣ Compare With ASGI\nFrameworks like FastAPI or async Django use Uvicorn (ASGI server).",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "6️⃣ Compare With ASGI\nFrameworks like FastAPI or async Django use Uvicorn (ASGI server).",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "t2sj21fZxW4uFS3CXaOkj",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1950.8569108576967,
      "y": 4250.581997843081,
      "width": 385,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFF",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 845179333,
      "version": 170,
      "versionNonce": 1355152409,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773235365038,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ASGI allows:\n1 worker → many concurrent requests\n\nWorker\n   Request1 waiting DB\n   Request2 processing\n   Request3 waiting API\n   Request4 processing\n\nBecause of async event loop.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ASGI allows:\n1 worker → many concurrent requests\n\nWorker\n   Request1 waiting DB\n   Request2 processing\n   Request3 waiting API\n   Request4 processing\n\nBecause of async event loop.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "DICblCUfv8yNX59XjDUCd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1897.5990983576967,
      "y": 4565.796841593081,
      "width": 286,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFG",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 673252075,
      "version": 163,
      "versionNonce": 1321275641,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773235365038,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "7️⃣ Real Production Example\nTypical Django WSGI setup:",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "7️⃣ Real Production Example\nTypical Django WSGI setup:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "WE8PyfjCSV55wLvcLRCjr",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1957.0170671076967,
      "y": 4637.894497843081,
      "width": 275,
      "height": 300,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFH",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1628383211,
      "version": 175,
      "versionNonce": 172394969,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773235365038,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Nginx\n  ↓\nGunicorn (8 workers)\n  ↓\nDjango\n\nCapacity:\n    8 concurrent requests\n\nIf 100 users hit the API:\n    8 active\n    92 waiting",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Nginx\n  ↓\nGunicorn (8 workers)\n  ↓\nDjango\n\nCapacity:\n    8 concurrent requests\n\nIf 100 users hit the API:\n    8 active\n    92 waiting",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aGY8El9ACFM1GA4JUtnO6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1891.8803483576967,
      "y": 4990.906216593081,
      "width": 1067,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFI",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1473058859,
      "version": 161,
      "versionNonce": 745137849,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773235365038,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "8️⃣ Simple Interview Answer\n\nIn WSGI synchronous workers, one worker handles one request at a time. Concurrency is achieved by\n running multiple workers or threads.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "8️⃣ Simple Interview Answer\n\nIn WSGI synchronous workers, one worker handles one request at a time. Concurrency is achieved by\n running multiple workers or threads.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
